# Dom4j
Dom4j is flexible XML framework for Java.

## Download
* [dom4j-1.6.1](https://github.com/dom4j/dom4j/releases/tag/dom4j_1_6_1) for Java 1.4
* dom4j-2.0.0 (beta) for Java 1.5+

## Sources
Sources are available on [GitHub](https://github.com/dom4j/dom4j).
